                        "content": "The nurse is caring for a client who is on bed rest as part of aneurysm precautions. The nurse would plan to avoid taking which action when giving respiratory care to this client?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nWith aneurysm precautions, any activity that could raise the client's intracranial pressure (ICP) is avoided. For this reason, activities such as straining, coughing, blowing the nose, and even sneezing are avoided whenever possible. The other interventions (repositioning, deep breathing, and incentive spirometry) do not provide added risk of increasing ICP and are beneficial in reducing the respiratory complications of bed rest.",
                        "id": "234fbd63327c46c3a46d5ff3b04c75a0",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "f7de60ea5e9948ebbb7cf69ddb6c1360",
                                "content": "Keep the window blinds open."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "f6b7dde0b94a4ed9981969f6436bc73e",
                                "content": "Turn on a small spotlight above the client's head."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "7c836cc3f4ae4c93868f9f6e54a13365",
                                "content": "Make sure the door to the room is open at all times."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "0499cfee5e9d451d9cc4d1318fc29345",
                                "content": "Prohibit or limit the use of a radio or television and reading."
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
