                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The nurse develops a plan of care for a client with a brain aneurysm who will be placed on aneurysm precautions. Which interventions would be included in the plan? Select all that apply.",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAneurysm precautions include placing the client on bed rest in a quiet setting. The use of lights is kept to a minimum to prevent environmental stimulation. The nurse needs to monitor the blood pressure and note any changes that could indicate rupture. Any activity, such as pushing, pulling, sneezing, or straining, that increases the blood pressure or impedes venous return from the brain is prohibited. The nurse provides physical care to minimize increases in blood pressure. Visitors, radio, television, and reading materials are restricted or limited. Stimulants, such as nicotine and coffee and other caffeine-containing products, are prohibited. Decaffeinated coffee or tea may be used.",
                        "id": "202b2fba3625478e875468baea916474",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "0b3791d2a2b73c2b1666162108e0e6ce",
                                "content": "Provide physical aspects of care."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "70609373ba2c6131f46d1160e8c209e8",
                                "content": "Prevent pushing or straining activities."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "97b3a707d101cbd45f56c1dfb5bb80b6",
                                "content": "Limit caffeinated coffee to 1 cup per day."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "7f622268d74d186e91b6ac624204c01e",
                                "content": "Keep the lights on in the client's room."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "12cc33064617a42f961489f2b5dca71c",
                                "content": "Maintain the head of the bed at 15 degrees."
                            }
                        ],
